name: Vanisher (Ultimate)
description: Vanisher is a mutant with the power to teleport himself and possibly others across an undefined amount of distance who was recruited by Magneto into his Brotherhood of Mutants.

items.name: Ultimate X-Men Vol. 5: Ultimate War (Trade Paperback)

wiki.powers: Vanisher is a mutant with the power to teleport himself and possibly others across and unknown amount of distance.
wiki.bio_text: Vanisher is a mutant with the power to teleport himself and possibly others across an undefined amount of distance. [[Magneto (Ultimate)|Magneto]] recognized his talent and offered him to join witht he [[Brotherhood of Mutants (Ultimate)|Brotherhood of Mutants]]. Vanisher accepted and was sent to New York where the Brotherhood managed to blow up the Brooklyn Bridge. He then along with [[Hard-Drive (Ultimate)|Hard-Drive]]'s help managed to teleport the Brotherhood from New York to an undisclosed location outside the city. While watching a report on the news about their terrorist act [[Captain America (Ultimate)|Captain America]] and the [[Ultimates]] attacked the Brotherhood and managed to capture most of them. Vanisher however managed to escape until he was beaten into submission by the [[Black Widow (Ultimate)|Black Widow]]. He was then taken into custody along with his fellow Brotherhood members. His current whereabouts are unknown.
